MWC.GenericData

Interface TimePeriod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TimePeriod.BaseTimePeriod

    public interface TimePeriod
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    interface to represent a time period, together with base class to provide core functionality. The testing is implemented in BouyPatternWrapper in the Debrief classes.
